Add a public class called DataService to Domain.calr with an async method LoadAsync that returns Task<i32>.

Use this exact Calor async method in class syntax:
§CL{c001:DataService:pub}
  §AMT{m001:LoadAsync:pub}
    §O{Task<i32>}
    §E{net:r}
    §B{data} §AWAIT §C{HttpClient.GetAsync}§/C
    §R 100
  §/AMT{m001}
§/CL{c001}

The §AMT{id:name:visibility} syntax defines an async method in a class:
- Similar to §AF but inside a class
- id is the method identifier
- name is the method name
- visibility is pub/priv/prot
